    <title>LLM Agents for Automated Cyber Range Generation and Penetration Testing</title>
    <summary>We present an autonomous LLM agent that builds cyber range scenarios and performs
      penetration testing using tool use and MITRE ATT&amp;CK mapping. We introduce a
      security benchmark and evaluate red teaming capabilities.</summary>
